msgctxt "sn29.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 29 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 29 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Nāgavagga "
msgstr "1. Dragons "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn29.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Dutiyauposathasutta "
msgstr "4. Sabbath (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.242, sc1
msgctxt "sn29.4:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.4:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha … and asked him, "

msgctxt "sn29.4:1.3"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo, yena m’idhekacce jalābujā nāgā uposathaṃ upavasanti vossaṭṭhakāyā ca bhavantī”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, what is the cause, what is the reason why some womb-born dragons keep the sabbath, having transformed their bodies?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn29.4:1.4"
msgid "(Sabbaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.) "
msgstr "(All should be told in full.) "

msgctxt "sn29.4:1.5"
msgid "“Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhu, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo, yena m’idhekacce jalābujā nāgā uposathaṃ upavasanti vossaṭṭhakāyā ca bhavantī”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn29.4:1.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

